STATE
v.
Timothy Lee CREED. No. 493P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2009. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, Garland N. Yates, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 4th day of November 2008 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review or in the Alternative a Remedial Writ":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 5th day of February 2009."
